thread.title: Susan Quinn

author: Susan Quinn
title: Susan Quinn
text: Darneil was incredibly helpful, professional, friendly, and polite. He made the experience of selling my car hassle-free and worth it. He explained each step and made sure to answer any questions and provide a positive experience. He was very knowledgeable and straightforward about the entire process and not at all pushy. I had a really positive experience and would recommend the Elmwood Park branch to anyone!
